import mentors from "./dataSchool"; const [zeyd, angela] = mentors; const { name: [zeydName], branch: [zeydBranch], contact: { tel: [zeydTel], email: [zeydEmail], adres: [zeydAdres] }, experience:[zeydExperience] } = zeyd; function App2() { return (
# Name Branch Tel Email Adres Experience
1 {zeyd.name} {zeydBranch} {zeydTel} {zeydEmail} {zeydAdres} {zeyd}
2 {angela.name}
); } export default App2;
